{
  "texts": [
    "In Sect. 3, an overview of common datasets is given in chronological order of their creation.",
    "In Sect. 4, a comprehensive discussion is presented concerning the possible linkages that exist between both the NER dataset and the mainstream NER techniques.",
    "In Sect. 5, all the above work is integrated to predict the future trends of datasets in general.",
    "TaxonomyAs research on named entity recognition continues, an understanding of the development and evolution of NER datasets has become an integral part of this research.",
    "This section provides a chronological overview of the common NER datasets presented since the MUC-6 conference."
  ]
}